    <h3>Scientific Computing and Model Exploration</h3>
    <p>This course introduces the fundamental principles and tools of modern scientific computing for studying complex systems through simulation. It covers general concepts of computational modeling, data analysis, and machine learning, along with techniques for running large-scale computational experiments.</p>
